{"tid":1053482,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"11歲男割包皮　尿道被誤封！3天無法排尿","createTime":"2019-03-09T06:08:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-10T07:45:25.000Z","uid":130626,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"4c4248d2f83340c6ff2fa27b5cb44e3284d4d7c5","tid":1053482,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T06:08:24.000Z","msg":"南非一名11歲男孩去割包皮，結果手術後尿道被縫合起來，導致他3天不能尿尿，到其他家醫院就診後，才把尿道解封。<br />\n據《dailysun》報導，2月16日，南非一名男孩給在靠近布里茨(Brits)的非政府組織「JPS Africa」割包皮，但沒想到醫生在他的龜頭縫了幾針，導致他無法尿尿，男孩的母親帶他回診，但是醫生只要他回家拆掉繃帶就好，男孩母親說「醫院只拍了陰莖幾張照片，並給了止痛藥就要我們回來了」。<br />\n於是他們到另一間醫院進行檢查，醫生看到後大驚「是誰這樣做的？」之後立即用導尿管幫忙排尿，母親說「裝了2個2公升的瓶子」。2月23日醫療團隊再去探望男孩，表示「男孩傷口癒合的很好」。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190309/640_88b13a644bd6e23604cd313e6a9e3d6f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190309%2F640_88b13a644bd6e23604cd313e6a9e3d6f.jpg&h=f7ebdf4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當事人背影。翻攝自dailysun"},{"pid":"3d768ef8fe33342b9acf92a0e662bd1b40f815aa","tid":1053482,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T06:09:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c7f2073c6da5100c56300b02d9ef0148f0de86b","tid":1053482,"uid":186844,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T06:09:26.000Z","msg":"仆街醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec77275f985af81c5b4819ab331894b3a443ca8f","tid":1053482,"uid":130879,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T06:10:38.000Z","msg":"個腎咁就無左"},{"pid":"9769a3d88eb06e1130e133cafc26b024abf2cefa","tid":1053482,"uid":167465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T06:17:08.000Z","msg":"痴撚線 咩醫生嚟"},{"pid":"019ea3c14788bf74716208cb56987bc789aa507e","tid":1053482,"uid":47160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T06:20:29.000Z","msg":"